comments:
I got the following NPE on startup. What I did:

- took the integration build
- replaced my plugins with it
- didn't turn on the two team UI plugins
- started up.

There are a few things going on here so it may be just a one-shot problem 
between old and new.  For example, I may have had Team plugins in my plugin 
directory already -- I don't recall.
